Correspondence Pilot Summary

2024-08-14

Pilot Basics

Messages sent

So far

  • we have sent out 362 messages

  • 126 of those messages received responses

  • We’ve gotten 160 responses overall, due to some messages getting multiple responses

Bank-side data

We have reached out to 50 banks and financial institutions. So far they have received somewhere between 1 and 16 messages. The pilot design was for all banks to receive somewhere between 5 and 20 messages.

Characteristics of senders

Bank responses

Response rates by bank. Most banks never respond, but there is still lots of variation.

It doesn’t look like banks stop responding after only a few messages.

Frequency, on the other hand, does seem to matter.
